high_descs: Turn around and go to the left side of the sink to your left.
Pick up the soap dispenser on the left corner of the sink.
Turn around and go past the shower on your right to the bathroom sink on your right.
Place the soap dispenser in the drawer, under the sink, closest to the shower.
anns.task_desc: Put the soap dispenser in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and make a left to walk to the sinks with the bottle next to them.
Pick up the bottle on the left of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the sinks on the left side of the shower.
Put the bottle in the lower right-hand drawer below the sinks.
anns.task_desc: Move a bottle to a drawer to the left of the shower.

high_descs: Turn around, walk forward to the mat on the floor, then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the bottle of soap on the left side of the counter.
Turn left and walk to the black drawers under the sink.
Put the bottle of soap in the bottom right drawer, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move a bottle of soap from a counter to a drawer.
